      &lt;img alt="An early version of the NES Hub in front of a European version of the NES console." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/o38QBd0bG_k8wrtGezSdAce_8AM=/0x0:1930x1287/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73642279/nes3.0.jpg" /&gt;
