      &lt;img alt="The GeForce RTX logo on the Nvidia GeForce RTX 4090 Founders Edition." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/xwuGmNGdI8JwH4PO6O8UKFDicVE=/7x0:2034x1351/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73642150/226321_Nvidia_RTX_4090_twarren_0013.0.jpg" /&gt;
